Gérard Pique, footballer and ex-lover of Colombian singer Shakira, has shared a picture of himself and his new girlfriend, Clara. This comes after Shakira lashed out at him and his new girlfriend, Clara, in her new track ‘Out of Your League‘ which hit 63 million views in 24 hours, making it the most-watched new Latin song on YouTube. Pique shared a picture of himself and his girlfriend via his Instagram account on Wednesday without any caption. ALSO READ: Shakira’s song dissing ex, Pique breaks Latin YouTube viewing records Shakira and Pique were together for more than a decade and have two sons They never married, and Shakira did not share her estimated $300 million fortune with Pique. 